              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 7v10a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2-2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Trailers & Equipment</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Protection for trailers, attachments, and mobile equipment used in your business.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>• Cargo trailers</li>
            <li>• Equipment trailers</li>
            <li>• Semi-trailers</li>
            <li>• Utility trailers</li>
            <li>• Mobile equipment</li>
          </ul>
