              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-navy-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 mt-1">
                <span class="text-white text-sm font-bold">3</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Comprehensive Coverage</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Protects against theft, vandalism, fire, weather damage, and other non-collision losses.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-navy-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 mt-1">
                <span class="text-white text-sm font-bold">4</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Medical Payments</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Covers medical expenses for you and your passengers regardless of fault.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">Additional Protection</h3>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
